&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify process gaps and pain points from end-user and stakeholder perspectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Redesign workflows to improve efficiency, transparency and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop clear SOPs, guidelines, and training materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initiate and discuss system development requests with IT.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support solution design, testing and data validation for system-related projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
