&lt;li lang=&quot;en-US&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Aptos; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;Shift &amp;amp; Resource Governance:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Manage shift schedules to ensure 24/7 operational coverage, including holiday planning and emergency backup coordination. Monitor real-time ticket queues to balance workload effectively across the team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
